  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Empower and educate girls free of sexual violence</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Fundacion Idea Dignidad works with girls and their families to eradicate sexual violence and forced pregnancy. We develop training and accompaniment through art to increase their self-esteem, knowledge of their rights and create protective environments in which they can develop their skills and life projects. With this project, girls, their families and caregivers will have access to psychosocial support, didactic material and education about rights through art and play.</narrative>
  </description>
